# SecureFlow uses two independent .env files, not this root one:
#   • backend/.env   — see backend/.env.example (FastAPI, DB, Redis, JWT, ML, chain)
#   • frontend/.env.local — see frontend/.env.local.example (API + WS URLs)
#
# This file is kept only as a pointer. Copy the per-service examples instead:
#   cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
#   cp frontend/.env.local.example frontend/.env.local
